"Clear find
nnoremap <silent> <Leader>fc :CommandTFlush<CR>

" Search for the current selection (redux)
xnoremap * :<C-u>call <SID>VSetSearch()<CR>/<C-R>=@/<CR><CR>
xnoremap # :<C-u>call <SID>VSetSearch()<CR>?<C-R>=@/<CR><CR>

"Eclim
nnoremap <Leader>jt :JUnit<CR> 
nnoremap <Leader>jb :ProjectBuild<CR> 
